                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Saldırı</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">1</span> <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Toprak Hasarı </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">verir</span></p>",
